        dc:description           "Figure 11. Gymnopus foliiphilus. Pileal hairs. Standard bars = 10 µm. TFB 2800 (TENN-F- 49363)." , "Figure 16. Gymnopus foliiphilus. Caulocystidia from lower stipe. Standard bars = 10 µm. TFB 2800 (TENN-F- 49363)." , "Figure 15. Gymnopus foliiphilus. Caulocystidia from upper stipe. Standard bars = 10 µm. TFB 2800 (TENN-F- 49363)." , "Figure 13. Gymnopus foliiphilus. Pleurocystidia and basidia. A-D Pleurocystidia E-H Basidia. Standard bars = 10 µm. TFB 11555 (TENN-F- 59441)." , "Figure 12. Gymnopus foliiphilus. Pileipellis elements. A-C Encrusted hyphae D Hyphae showing secondary septa E Gelatinized hyphal walls F, G Lobate side branches. Standard bars = 10 µm. TFB 2800 (TENN-F- 49363)." , "Figure 10. Gymnopus foliiphilus. Basidiomata. Standard bars = 10 mm." , "Figure 14. Gymnopus foliiphilus. Basidiospores. Standard bar = 5 µm. A = TFB 11608 (TENN-F- 59641); B = TFB 14322 (TENN-F- 68183)." ;
